descript.abstract: [Metadata] 2020 Census County Boundaries, with population, for the State of Hawaii, excluding northwest Hawaiian Islands and clipped to the coastline. Source: US Census Bureau, September 2021. For additional information about this layer, please refer to metadata at https://files.hawaii.gov/dbedt/op/gis/data/county20.pdf or contact Hawaii Statewide GIS Program, Office of Planning and Sustainable Development, State of Hawaii; PO Box 2359, Honolulu, Hi. 96804; (808) 587-2846; email: gis@hawaii.gov; Website: https://planning.hawaii.gov/gis.
